search_results.title: Dave Logan (writer)
search_results.snippet: David C. Logan (born 1968) is an American author and professor. He is best known for his book Tribal Leadership which was a New York Times Bestseller .

search_results.title: Dave Logan | Leadership Speaker
search_results.snippet: Dr. Dave Logan is the bestselling author of Tribal Leadership (#1 New York Times) , The Three Laws of Performance, and The Best Medicine.

search_results.title: F. Donald Logan
search_results.snippet: Francis Donald Logan FSA FRHistS (born March 9, 1930, died February 22, 2022) was an American historian who was Professor of History at Emmanuel College.
